        <h2>Tactics</h2>
        <p>
            The great thing about football is there are a million different ways to play it. 
            It's the job of the manager to mould the way a team plays, and you only have to take one look at the elite end of the sport to see differences in the way team’s set-up and play football. 
            There are many formations and tactics being employed be various teams, with hundreds of subtle distinctions branching off from them. 
        </p>
